# Oracle / LRB / PRO

Use this when the project enables LRB Oracle or human-run ChatGPT PRO review.

Workspace rule source:

- `..\..\System\docs\oracle.md`
- `..\..\System\docs\oracle-milestone-pack.md`
- `..\..\System\docs\oracle-runner-procedure.md`
- `..\..\System\docs\services.md`

## Contract

- Local Review Bridge is the preferred local-folder review route when it passes
  ON/status preflight.
- ZIP or sanitized packs are fallback routes.
- PRO review is human-run unless the user explicitly authorizes browser
  interaction for a bounded test.
- Oracle advice is classified as ADOPT, PARTIAL_ADOPT, REJECT, DEFER, or
  NEEDS_HUMAN before it changes the repo.

## Forbidden

- Do not read credentials, browser state, or raw local databases.
- Do not add paid polling, provider refresh loops, or repository mutations from
  the browser/oracle runner.
